<div id="pf3bf2" class="pf w65 h237" data-page-no="3bf2"><div class="pc pc3bf2 w65 h237"><div class="t maec x3a h108 y583 ff3 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ARE THE TESTIMONY </div><div class="t m278 x45 h108 y2dd ff3 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MESSAGES </div><div class="t mf98 x6e h108 y2ff ff3 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">GETTING </div><div class="t m12b3 x8f h108 y31b ff3 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THROUGH? </div><div class="t ma73 x0 h35 ydd6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as probationary time comes to an end, as history comes to its last chapter, as </div><div class="t m128 x0 h35 y571 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ finishes His work for the salvation of men, and as closing events in the </div><div class="t m51e x0 h35 y13a1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">great controversy bring us ever nearer to the grand consummation of all things </div><div class="t m43c xc4 h35 y40c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">earthly. </div><div class="t m3e7 x27 h35 y9f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We have every reason to rejoice as Seventh-day Adventists in the abundant </div><div class="t m581 x0 h35 y66e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">provision made by God Himself for our salvation. He loves us with a tender love. </div><div class="t m163 x0 h35 ye8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He is kind and good and gentle. He has anticipated our every need, and has </div><div class="t m748 xb7 h35 y1750 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given us the help we must have at every turn in life&apos;s way. He is ready to </div><div class="t mddb x1a3 h35 y1206 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fit </div><div class="t m2c9 x0 h35 yb1f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us for His kingdom. May each and every one of us be molded and fashioned </div><div class="t m335 xb7 h35 y712 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">according to His own divine pattern. He wants you and me in His presence </div><div class="t me1a x0 h35 y78b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">throughout eternity.&quot; Page 320. </div><div class="t m1bc0 x0 h5 y1259 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON OUTLINE </div><div class="t m23f xb7 h5 y11